The presence of Fall Guys characters in the image references the popular video game, making it relevant to contemporary pop culture.
The image features intricate details in the characters' costumes and expressions, which is contrary to the simplicity often associated with minimalistic art.
The image exudes a sense of wholesomeness and innocence, characteristic of the family-friendly appeal of Fall Guys.
While the characters may inhabit fantastical worlds within the game, the image itself does not present a dreamlike or illogical composition that defines surrealism.
